	<p>
		My posts on this website are a means for me to share my ideas and my inspirations
		with you.  I try not to post tutorials, howtos or step-by-step guides.  Instead I
		try to post about the ideas themselves, hoping they will inspire you to do greater
		things than I am capable of.
	</p>
	
	<p>
		Generally speaking, what inspires me personally is making the amazing out of the
		unlikely.  I think that's why web development is so appealing to me:  the medium of
		the web is relatively so limited, yet people manage to do mind-blowing things with it.
		I hope some of my material inspires you to do the same.
	
	</p>
	
