	<h3>INMSA's Image Library</h3>

	<p>
		While at Independent Online I had the opportunity to develop the group's
		image library, a system which archived photographs used in production for future
		use. The system allows you to search for photos based on pre-defined IPTC
		information. An interesting challenge in developing this system was to ensure
		that images which were re-used in production did not get re-imported.
	</p>

